    "TransUNet, like U-Net, has become a popular network for medical image segmentation.",
    "Because of the complexities of medical image segmentation tasks, high-quality manually labeled datasets can only be produced on a small scale.",
    "To achieve better performance on medical image datasets, it is necessary to continuously optimize the application of transformer in the encoder/decoder network.",
